# Server Types

elif node() == 'MyBook-Staging':   
    SERVER_TYPE = 'staging'
elif node() == 'Marks-iMac.local':

elif node() == 'seaman-macbook.local':
    SERVER_TYPE = 'macbook'
else:  
    SERVER_TYPE = 'dev'


# Type of server for this machine

# Select Domain that matches Hostname
